- 'Appetite for power' refers to the average power consumption of the devices;
- 'Throughout the year 2020' indicates the date range from '2020-01-01' to '2020-12-31';
- 'Exceeds 100 watts' means the average power consumption is greater than 100 watts.

- "energy usage soars above the average" refers to days where the total energy consumption is greater than the average total energy consumption across all days;
- "total daily energy consumption" is the sum of energy consumed by all devices on a specific day;
- "average daily power usage" is the average power consumption of all devices on a specific day.

